<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    {% seo "" %}
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/coldark.css" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/favicon.ico" />
    <script
      async
      data-token="MWFWWD5X1WEC"
      data-respect-dnt
      data-no-cookie
      src="https://cdn.splitbee.io/sb.js"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="p-5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <a
        class="
          font-semibold
          text-teal-700
          rounded-sm
          dark:text-teal-400
          focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
          dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-800 dark:focus:ring-pink-400
          focus:ring-pink-700
        "
        href="/"
        >Devlog</a
      >
    </nav>
    <main class="my-8 md:px-8 grid grid-template-main">
      <div class="text-sm col-start-3 col-end-4">
        <section class="mb-12 space-y-2">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-400"
              >You've found my devlog!</strong
            >
            Here I'm trying to collect ideas and thoughts, new findings, and
            reminders regarding software development. I see it as a
            <a
              class="
                text-indigo-600
                rounded-sm
                dark:text-indigo-400
                focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
                dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-pink-400
                focus:ring-pink-700
              "
              href="https://www.buildingasecondbrain.com/"
              >second brain</a
            >
            for all things related to development. It's also also a way for me
            to practice
            <a
              class="
                text-teal-700
                rounded-sm
                dark:text-teal-400
                group
                focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
                dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-pink-400
                focus:ring-pink-700
              "
              href="/pages/learning-in-public"
            >
              <span class="text-gray-500 group-hover:text-teal-900">[[</span
              >Learning in public<span
                class="text-gray-500 group-hover:text-teal-900"
                >]]</span
              ></a
            >.
          </p>
          <p>
            The content is created in
            <a
              class="
                text-indigo-600
                rounded-sm
                dark:text-indigo-400
                focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
                dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-pink-400
                focus:ring-pink-700
              "
              href="https://logseq.com/"
              >Logseq</a
            >, exported to JSON and then generated as static HTML.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm currently on paternal leave for the rest of 2021. Updates might
            not happen that often.
          </p>
        </section>
        {% block content %}
        {{ content | safe }}
        {% endblock %}
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="mb-12 text-sm text-center">
      Built by
      <a
        class="
          text-teal-700
          rounded-sm
          dark:text-teal-400
          group
          focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
          dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900
          focus:ring-pink-400 focus:ring-pink-700
        "
        href="https://twitter.com/rnattochdag"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        >@rnattochdag</a
      >. Code at
      <a
        class="
          text-teal-700
          rounded-sm
          dark:text-teal-400
          group
          focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
          dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 dark:focus:ring-pink-400
          focus:ring-pink-700
        "
        href="https://github.com/believer/devlog"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        >GitHub</a
      >.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
